Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:33.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不知不覺間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:39.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在虛幻的夢境中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:45.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失去了言語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:50.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目光閃動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:56.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在火燄之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:24:01.75,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓約的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:06.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:12.18,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓這份祈禱到達吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:17.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過深深的車轍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:23.57,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到這个世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.74,0:24:29.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}堅守誓言到底
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.35,0:24:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到六太呼唤  人影转过身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.09,0:24:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微笑着站了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.69,0:24:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二国记  第四十一话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东之海神  西之沧海  第一章
